<svg width="0" height="0"  viewBox="0 0 1 1" preserveAspectRatio="none" class="my-0" style="position:absolute; pointer-events: none;" >
  <defs>
    <clipPath id="myClip" clipPathUnits="objectBoundingBox">
        <path  d="M0,0v0.9c0,0,0.2,0.1,0.5,0S1,1,1,1V0H0z"/>
    </clipPath>
        <clipPath id="myClipFooter" clipPathUnits="objectBoundingBox">
        <path  d="M1,1V0c0,0-0.2,0.1-0.5,0S0,0.1,0,0.1V1H1z"/>
    </clipPath>
  </defs>
</svg>

<header class="position-relative" style="top:-48px; padding-bottom:200px;">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="jumbotron bg-transparent">
      <h1>makyma</h1>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-12 col-md-8 col-lg-6">
          <span>Le compagnon pour ta transition responsable.</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col">
          <%= simple_form_for :search, url: products_path, method: "GET", html: { class: "my-5" } do |f| %>
            <%= f.input :title, input_html: {class:''}, label:false, placeholder: 'exemple : sac plastique, film alimentaire...' %>
            <%# <%= f.button :submit, class: "btn btn-light" %>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col">
          <p>Tu as pris conscience de ton impact écologique et tu souhaites le réduire sans changer tes habitudes. Découvre les alternatives vertes aux produits de ton quotidien, et adopte un comportement éco-responsable.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<div class="container position-relative" style="top: -250px">
  <div class="row shadow bg-dark justify-content-center px-4 pb-5 pt-4" style="border-radius: 13px;">
    <div class="col-12 text-center text-info mb-4">
      <span style="font-weight: 600;">Comment ça marche ?</span>
    </div>
    <div class="col-10 col-md-4">
      <div class="card border-0" style="border-radius: 13px;">
        <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column align-items-center">
          <p class="position-absolute text-info" style="font-weight: 700; top: 15px; left:25px">1</p>
          <%= image_tag "thinking.png", class:'mb-4', style:"width:50%;", alt: "Émoticône de la reflexion, visage qui réfléchit" %>
          <p class="card-title text-center text-secondary font-weight-normal">Choisis un article de ton quotidien que tu souhaites remplacer.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-10 col-md-4 mt-5 mt-md-0">
      <div class="card border-0" style="border-radius: 13px;">
        <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column align-items-center">
          <p class="position-absolute text-info" style="font-weight: 700; top: 15px; left:25px">2</p>
          <%= image_tag "recycle.png", class:'mb-4', style:"width:50%", alt: "Icone symbolisant le recyclage" %>
          <p class="card-title text-center text-secondary font-weight-normal">Découvre les alternatives écologiques à celui-ci.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-10 col-md-4 mt-5 mt-md-0">
      <div class="card border-0" style="border-radius: 13px;">
        <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column align-items-center">
          <p class="position-absolute text-info" style="font-weight: 700; top: 15px; left:25px">3</p>
          <%= image_tag "hit.png", class:'mb-4', style:"width:50%", alt: "Icone symbolisant le jeu de fléchette" %>
          <p class="card-title text-center text-secondary font-weight-normal">Adopte la solution qui te correspond le mieux !</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>



  <div class="row position-relative mb-4" style="bottom: -120px">
    <div class="col text-center">
      <span class="text-info"style="font-weight: 600;">Les catégories</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row justify-content-center position-relative no-gutters" style="bottom: -120px">
    <% @categories.each do |category| %>
      <div class="col-7 my-3 col-sm-5 m-sm-3 col-md-3 m-md-4">
        <div class="card shadow border-0" style="border-radius: 13px;">
          <%= link_to category do %>
          <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column align-items-center">
            <%= image_tag category.image, class:'m-5', style:"width:60%", alt: "Icône symbolisant la catégorie "+category.title %>
            <p class="card-title font-weight-normal text-secondary"><%= category.title %></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      <% end %>
      </div>
    <% end %>
  </div>

  <div class="row justify-content-around">
    <% if can? :manage, @category %>
      <button type="button" class="col-lg-2 btn btn-outline-primary" style="border-radius: 35px;"><%= link_to 'Nouvelle catégorie', new_category_path %></button>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>
